{"tid":696910,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新垣結衣化身蛋黃妹 慵懶滾床撒嬌","createTime":"2018-06-10T13:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T15:32:02.000Z","uid":9573,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"27149f0c8dc66f6b9513d84e5a78acdb8325da1e","tid":696910,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"29歲日本女星新垣結衣前年演出日劇《月薪嬌妻》暴紅，被封為「國民老婆」。她在最新的泡麵廣告中化身「蛋黃妹」，跟著小雞躺在床上慵懶翻滾、還對著鏡頭撒嬌，萌樣讓粉絲融化。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7gLq1yruq3MyC2P8suYrdA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/news_tvbs_com_tw_938/256277fd576026ed954aa325597f3f52\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F7gLq1yruq3MyC2P8suYrdA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnews_tvbs_com_tw_938%2F256277fd576026ed954aa325597f3f52&h=6c8ec76a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟著小雞躺在床上一動也不動，日本女星新垣結衣為泡麵拍廣告，還對著鏡頭撒嬌，萌樣讓粉絲融化，慵懶模樣也讓新垣結衣笑說6小時的拍攝一半時間都在被子裡，心想「這樣真的沒問題嗎？」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/AAyrbQM.img?h=1249&amp;w=799&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=549&amp;y=524\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FAAyrbQM.img%3Fh%3D1249%26w%3D799%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D549%26y%3D524&h=2bf160de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n29歲的新垣結衣前年演出《月薪嬌妻》暴紅，更被封為「國民老婆」，廣告邀約不斷。穿白色T恤搭牛仔短褲難得大秀白皙長腿，新垣結衣先前為洗髮精拍廣告，隨風吹出一頭亂髮吸引網友狂讚，留言「看不出快30歲了」、「簡直美到像天使」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/AAypGsw.img?h=400&amp;w=500&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FAAypGsw.img%3Fh%3D400%26w%3D500%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df&h=c7a9444d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n還有為合作13年的巧克力品牌拍新廣告，她戴上眼鏡化身巧克力老師，更變身「布穀鳥」報時，用超可愛的方式讓觀眾知道在什麼時候，吃巧克力最適合，模樣萌翻引起廣大粉絲迴響，見證國民老婆的魅力。"},{"pid":"4beb6a4b185f41e6bf40b09443fa366016b36358","tid":696910,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:39:12.000Z","msg":"沙拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42df553a8aa03a0d48ba9aa675dd08dd163c1af5","tid":696910,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:40:53.000Z","msg":"2g"},{"pid":"3b4f0f684a30665945948dd19613f06206e7ef7a","tid":696910,"uid":106204,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:42:07.000Z","msg":"千雪呢?"},{"pid":"5c62786fa2986f2bafc554ec13ee25d897c0dbd1","tid":696910,"uid":129660,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:42:31.000Z","msg":"長髮靚十倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63632cbb16adfb2899b77eb6588120176f0b00b3","tid":696910,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:52:00.000Z","msg":"...."},{"pid":"73575e8506e1fafe541eb8a04504730ef49d516d","tid":696910,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T15:24:57.000Z","msg":"沙拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f07ca070f00bcf6cb9f1d7855180e8dd6f39bd6","tid":696910,"uid":48294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T15:32:02.000Z","msg":"做咩塊面無啦啦多左咁多毛？"}]}